name: Fenoget 200 mg capsule
description: Fenofibrate is used along with a proper diet to help lower bad cholesterol and fats (such as LDL, triglycerides) and raise good cholesterol (HDL) in the blood. Fenofibrate works by increasing the natural substance (enzyme) that breaks down fats in the blood. Fenofibrate belongs to a group of medicines known as fibrates.
label: medicine
